Final issue! An epic, jaw-dropping finale you can't miss from Coheed and Cambria's Claudio Sanchez (The Amory Wars) and Chondra Echert (Kill Audio)! With the one man holding the key buried in chains, the two remaining human factions in zombie-filled New York City are ready for war. Will Ewing be able to escape his shackles and exact his revenge - or will a triumphant Lavoe finish what he started? All this in the pulse-pounding conclusion that redefines the zombie genre!
